Wildrider/Speedbreaker
---------------------------

Wildrider and Speedbreaker both get up. Wildrider draws his weapon and 
aims it, but Speedbreaker turns around, transforms, and drives off 
back towards base, mumbling something. "Ha ha, hey Dead-End, you're a 
worse leader than Motormaster".
